## Boolean-Based SQLi Payloads

### SID: 1000200 - OR 1=1 with comment
```bash
# Test 1: Basic OR 1=1
curl -X POST http://testlab.local/test-lab/login_vulnerable.php \
  -d "username=admin' OR 1=1 --&password=test"

# Expected Alert: SQL Injection - OR 1=1 with comment (SID:1000200)

# Test 2: With space variations
curl -X POST http://testlab.local/test-lab/login_vulnerable.php \
  -d "username=admin' OR 1 = 1 --&password=test"

# Test 3: Single quotes
curl -X POST http://testlab.local/test-lab/login_vulnerable.php \
  -d "username=admin' or 1=1 --&password=test"
