## Notes

- 🔴 **DO NOT** run destructive payloads (DROP, DELETE) on production databases
- ⏱️ Time-based payloads will cause the request to hang - this is expected
- 🛡️ The secure page (`login_secure.php`) should block all SQL injection attempts
- 📊 All attempts are logged to `login_attempts` table - view via test_dashboard.php
